OL,3,CMan arrested over Amy Doherty murder
OL,4,C'unfit for police interview'
OL,6,FA man arrested over the murder of a
OL,7,Fmother-of-two in Londonderry is
OL,8,Fcurrently unfit to be questioned, the
OL,9,FPSNI has said.
OL,11,FPolice launched a murder investigation
OL,12,Fafter officers were called to a
OL,13,Fproperty in the Summer Meadows Mews
OL,14,Farea of the city on Saturday and found
OL,15,F28-year-old Amy Doherty badly injured.
OL,17,FMs Doherty was taken to hospital where
OL,18,Fshe later died.
OL,20,FA 30-year-old man was arrested on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
