OL,3,CMan arrested over Amy Doherty murder
OL,4,C'unfit for police interview'
OL,6,FThe PSNI has confirmed the man is
OL,7,Freceiving medical treatment and is not
OL,8,Ffit for police interview.
OL,10,FMs Doherty's funeral will take place
OL,11,Fon Thursday.
